OL,3,CGreggs to put sandwiches and drinks
OL,4,Cbehind counter to tackle rise in
OL,5,Cshoplifting
OL,7,FGreggs says it will be removing all
OL,8,Fcold sandwiches and bottled drinks
OL,9,Ffrom its self-serve fridges and
OL,10,Fputting them behind the counter, in an
OL,11,Feffort to curb shoplifting.
OL,13,FThe bakery chain said the changes are
OL,14,Fbeing introduced on a trial basis at a
OL,15,Fsmall number of branches across the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,FIt follows a report by The Sun
OL,19,Fnewspaper, which showed thieves were
OL,20,Ftargeting some Greggs stores every 20
OL,21,Fminutes.
