OL,7,FA spokesperson for Greggs said: "This
OL,8,Fis one of a number of initiatives we
OL,9,Fare trialing across a handful of shops
OL,10,Fwhich are exposed to higher levels of
OL,11,Fanti-social behaviour.
OL,13,F"Customers can expect to see our full
OL,14,Frange of great value and tasty Greggs
OL,15,Ffavourites available from behind the
OL,16,Fcounter.
OL,18,F"The safety of our colleagues and
OL,19,Fcustomers remains our number one
OL,20,Fpriority."
