OL,7,FThe company is one of a number of
OL,8,Fretail stores reporting a rise in the
OL,9,Fnumber of crimes in recent years
OL,10,Fincluding violence against its staff
OL,11,Fand customers.
OL,13,FRetail crime is now at the highest
OL,14,Flevels ever since policing records
OL,15,Fbegan in March 2003 with over half a
OL,16,Fmillion offences in the last year
OL,17,Falone.
