OL,5,Cshoplifting
OL,7,FData from the Office for National
OL,8,FStatistics (ONS) showed shoplifting
OL,9,Foffences had increased by 20% from
OL,10,F429,873 offences last year, to 516,971
OL,11,Fthis year.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police previously
OL,14,Fsaid retail crime was "spiraling out
OL,15,Fof control" as data for London also
OL,16,Frose sharply with 90,000 incidents
OL,17,Frecorded in the last 12 months to
OL,18,FDecember 2024.
