OL,4,Cbehind counter to tackle rise in
OL,5,Cshoplifting
OL,7,FEarlier this year, boss Roisin Currie
OL,8,Falso said the business was testing new
OL,9,Finitiatives including high-security
OL,10,Fdoors, panic alarms and a system that
OL,11,Finstantly shares shoplifter images
OL,12,Fwith police, as well as introducing
OL,13,Fbody-worn cameras to staff members.
OL,15,FThe trial at Greggs is not expected to
OL,16,Fbe rolled out nationwide, but will be
OL,17,Fused to see how effective the new
OL,18,Fformat is and will inform future
OL,19,Finitiatives.
